          <p class="light-gray">Your Essential Skincare Set for Combination Skin</p>
          <br>
          <br>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>NicholsMD Mattifying SPF</strong><br>
                Protect your skin from UV damage while keeping excess shine under control. This lightweight, oil-free
                sunscreen offers broad-spectrum protection and a matte finish, perfect for minimizing the look of pores
