              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Retinol 0.3 by SkinCeuticals</strong><br>
                Promote cell turnover and refine skin texture with this gentle, beginner-friendly retinol. It reduces
                the appearance of enlarged pores and fine lines while keeping your skin smooth and youthful.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Pore Refining Pads</strong><br>
                Gently exfoliate and tighten pores with these easy-to-use pads. Infused with pore-minimizing
                ingredients, they help remove excess oil and impurities, keeping your skin balanced and clear.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Serum 10 by SkinCeuticals</strong><br>
                Defend your skin against environmental stress and early signs of aging with this lightweight vitamin C
                antioxidant serum. It brightens your complexion and supports firmer, smoother skin.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Cell Cycle Catalyst</strong><br>
                Boost your skin’s renewal process with this advanced treatment. It helps refine pores, smooth uneven
                texture, and improve skin clarity—giving you a youthful, glowing complexion.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Clarifying Clay Masque</strong><br>
                Detoxify and deeply cleanse your pores with this purifying clay mask. It draws out impurities, reduces
